{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"TLS","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/TLS","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>传输层安全性协议 (Transport Layer Security，缩写作 TLS)，它的前身是安全套接层 (Secure Sockets Layer，缩写作 SSL)，是一个被应用程序用来在网络中安全通信的 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Protocol\">protocol</a> （通讯协议），防止电子邮件、网页、消息以及其他协议被篡改或是窃听。</p>\n<p>所有现代浏览器都支持 TLS 协议，它们都要求服务器提供一个有效的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Glossary/Digital_certificate\">digital certificate</a>（数字证书）来确认身份以建立安全连接。如果客户端和服务器都能提供自己的数字证书，则它们可以互相认证。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本知识","title":"基本知识","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Security/Transport_Layer_Security\">传输层安全性协议</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.owasp.org/index.php/Transport_Layer_Protection_Cheat_Sheet\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">OWASP: 传输层保护备忘单</a></li>\n  <li>维基百科上的<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Transport_Layer_Security\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Transport Layer Security</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"协议规范","title":"协议规范","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc5246\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">RFC 5246</a> (传输层安全性协议，版本：1.2)</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"传输层安全性协议 (Transport Layer Security，缩写作 TLS)，它的前身是安全套接层 (Secure Sockets Layer，缩写作 SSL)，是一个被应用程序用来在网络中安全通信的 protocol （通讯协议），防止电子邮件、网页、消息以及其他协议被篡改或是窃听。","popularity":0.0002,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Transport Layer Security (TLS)","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"TLS","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Transport Layer Security (TLS)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"전송 계층 보안 (TLS)","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"TLS","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"TLS","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/glossary/tls","gi